1
00:00:47,960 --> 00:00:49,090
Something is wrong.

2
00:00:49,360 --> 00:00:50,290
Why am I so angry?

3
00:00:50,880 --> 00:00:54,400
Whatever. I'll teach this scoundrel a lesson first.

4
00:00:55,000 --> 00:00:55,800
What's wrong?

5
00:00:56,000 --> 00:00:58,000
There are strange voices in my head.

6
00:00:59,440 --> 00:01:00,360
My head hurts.

7
00:01:01,000 --> 00:01:02,000
Are you all right?

8
00:01:03,200 --> 00:01:04,040
I'm fine.

9
00:01:05,200 --> 00:01:08,060
Is he the Son of the Heavenly Emperor you mentioned?

10
00:01:11,080 --> 00:01:11,880
He's getting away.

11
00:01:11,880 --> 00:01:13,080
Should we follow him?

12
00:01:20,039 --> 00:01:20,840
General.

13
00:01:21,400 --> 00:01:22,330
Why are you here?

14
00:01:22,520 --> 00:01:24,039
Demons have infiltrated.

15
00:01:24,440 --> 00:01:25,970
Protect Ling'er and Diyun.

16
00:01:26,200 --> 00:01:27,930
I'll go take care of this trash.

17
00:01:27,960 --> 00:01:28,640
Yes, sir.

18
00:01:35,000 --> 00:01:35,920
Pastries!

19
00:01:36,520 --> 00:01:37,680
Take a look!

20
00:01:40,960 --> 00:01:42,240
Come and have a look!

21
00:01:42,360 --> 00:01:43,759
Freshly baked pastries!

22
00:01:44,400 --> 00:01:45,400
Sister Qingluan.

23
00:01:45,600 --> 00:01:46,560
I'm back.

24
00:01:47,160 --> 00:01:48,360
What took you so long?

25
00:01:48,400 --> 00:01:50,280
I bought you lots of delicious food.

26
00:01:50,280 --> 00:01:51,080
Try some.

27
00:01:51,440 --> 00:01:52,240
Okay.

28
00:01:55,560 --> 00:01:56,160
Qingluan.

29
00:01:56,840 --> 00:01:58,039
Take good care of Ling'er for me.

30
00:01:58,039 --> 00:01:58,800
Ling'er?

31
00:01:59,440 --> 00:01:59,840
Yes.

32
00:02:00,560 --> 00:02:01,560
She is my Ling'er.

33
00:02:02,040 --> 00:02:03,920
The Ling'er I picked up from the street...

34
00:02:03,920 --> 00:02:05,480
turns out to be the Dragon Princess.

35
00:02:05,480 --> 00:02:06,000
Yes.

36
00:02:06,640 --> 00:02:08,160
She has forgotten her past.

37
00:02:08,160 --> 00:02:09,680
I've sent Yueying to investigate.

38
00:02:09,680 --> 00:02:11,440
Okay, Brother. Go heal your wounds first.

39
00:02:11,440 --> 00:02:13,170
I will look after the princess.

40
00:02:23,120 --> 00:02:24,650
It's been a thousand years.

41
00:02:24,760 --> 00:02:28,480
My clan finally sees a glimmer of hope.

42
00:02:51,120 --> 00:02:51,920
Audacious demon!

43
00:02:51,920 --> 00:02:53,000
How dare you cause trouble here!

44
00:02:53,000 --> 00:02:54,079
You will die today!

45
00:02:59,880 --> 00:03:00,800
King Kunmi?

46
00:03:01,960 --> 00:03:03,520
I didn't know it was you.

47
00:03:03,680 --> 00:03:05,560
I won't disturb you then.

48
00:03:11,520 --> 00:03:12,360
So sorry.

49
00:03:13,000 --> 00:03:14,520
I didn't mean to.

50
00:03:15,280 --> 00:03:16,880
No need to call me King Kunmi.

51
00:03:17,000 --> 00:03:18,200
Just call me Yunyuan.

52
00:03:20,560 --> 00:03:22,800
That... wouldn't be appropriate.

53
00:03:27,680 --> 00:03:29,600
Why is my heart beating so fast?

54
00:03:30,840 --> 00:03:32,920
Could you let me go first?

55
00:03:35,120 --> 00:03:37,650
Ling'er, what on earth have you been through?

56
00:03:38,160 --> 00:03:40,160
How could you forget me completely?

57
00:03:41,160 --> 00:03:42,600
If you call me Yunyuan,

58
00:03:43,560 --> 00:03:44,840
I will let you go.

59
00:03:46,120 --> 00:03:47,720
Yunyuan.

60
00:03:49,440 --> 00:03:50,840
I said it.

61
00:03:51,200 --> 00:03:52,360
Can you let me go now?

62
00:03:55,320 --> 00:03:56,120
Ling'er.

63
00:03:57,560 --> 00:03:59,020
Do you remember anything?

64
00:04:00,040 --> 00:04:01,720
What should I remember?

65
00:04:02,840 --> 00:04:04,680
King Kunmi, what do you mean?

66
00:04:06,720 --> 00:04:08,320
Still calling me King Kunmi?

67
00:04:10,880 --> 00:04:11,880
What are you doing?

68
00:04:11,880 --> 00:04:13,000
You're hurting me.

69
00:04:13,120 --> 00:04:14,280
Let go first.

70
00:04:21,959 --> 00:04:22,840
Leave.

71
00:04:24,000 --> 00:04:25,040
Don't come back.

72
00:04:34,240 --> 00:04:35,480
Ridiculous.

73
00:04:35,560 --> 00:04:36,640
It was like this last time too.

74
00:04:36,640 --> 00:04:38,570
Is there something wrong with him?

75
00:04:41,200 --> 00:04:42,320
Yunyuan...

76
00:04:44,840 --> 00:04:46,840
Forget it. I can't remember anyway.

77
00:05:01,560 --> 00:05:03,120
Son of the Heavenly Emperor.

78
00:05:03,120 --> 00:05:04,160
Why is he here?

79
00:05:24,240 --> 00:05:26,400
Help! Someone!

80
00:05:26,800 --> 00:05:30,320
Someone is kidnapping a girl in broad daylight!

81
00:05:36,080 --> 00:05:37,360
Miss.

82
00:05:37,640 --> 00:05:38,800
Wake up, Miss.

83
00:06:06,120 --> 00:06:07,800
Miss, you're awake.

84
00:06:08,560 --> 00:06:09,840
Where am I?

85
00:06:10,600 --> 00:06:11,400
Sir.

86
00:06:11,560 --> 00:06:13,160
Did you save me?

87
00:06:13,400 --> 00:06:14,040
Oh.

88
00:06:15,680 --> 00:06:17,280
You don't know where this is?

89
00:06:18,320 --> 00:06:19,760
Of course not.

90
00:06:19,880 --> 00:06:21,280
I met bandits on the road.

91
00:06:21,320 --> 00:06:22,650
I ran blindly in a panic.

92
00:06:23,520 --> 00:06:26,280
Thank you for saving me, Sir.

93
00:06:29,600 --> 00:06:30,730
Think nothing of it.

94
00:06:31,520 --> 00:06:32,520
What is your name?

95
00:06:33,080 --> 00:06:34,140
Where are you from?

96
00:06:34,840 --> 00:06:35,440
I...

97
00:06:37,560 --> 00:06:38,420
Thank you, Sir.

98
00:06:42,400 --> 00:06:43,560
I...

99
00:06:44,000 --> 00:06:45,640
...am from out of town.

100
00:06:47,120 --> 00:06:48,440
I came to stay with relatives.

101
00:06:48,440 --> 00:06:50,159
But when I arrived, I found...

102
00:06:51,080 --> 00:06:52,520
...my family was gone.

103
00:06:53,040 --> 00:06:54,920
Then I was caught by bandits.

104
00:06:55,280 --> 00:06:56,640
They wanted to...

105
00:06:57,159 --> 00:07:00,440
...force me to marry the rich man's idiot son.

106
00:07:04,440 --> 00:07:05,240
Sir.

107
00:07:06,080 --> 00:07:07,560
Please have mercy.

108
00:07:07,880 --> 00:07:09,320
Please take me in.

109
00:07:09,480 --> 00:07:10,880
Give me a bite to eat.

110
00:07:11,760 --> 00:07:13,760
I can do laundry and cook.

111
00:07:14,000 --> 00:07:15,460
I can sweep the courtyard.

112
00:07:15,600 --> 00:07:16,860
I can wipe the windows.

113
00:07:17,040 --> 00:07:18,280
I can do anything.

114
00:07:21,120 --> 00:07:23,960
Those storybooks I read with my sister didn't go to waste.

115
00:07:23,960 --> 00:07:26,880
Acting so weak, I'll definitely be able to stay.

116
00:07:27,600 --> 00:07:30,330
I don't believe I can't handle a playboy like you.

117
00:07:30,680 --> 00:07:31,400
Wait.

118
00:07:31,920 --> 00:07:34,000
Why do I keep thinking about pranking him?

119
00:07:34,000 --> 00:07:37,400
I feel like if I don't prank him, my hatred won't subside.

120
00:07:38,840 --> 00:07:41,080
If I don't play a trick on Di Yun today,

121
00:07:41,200 --> 00:07:42,640
my name isn't Ao Ling.

122
00:07:43,120 --> 00:07:44,120
Who is Ao Ling?

123
00:07:44,800 --> 00:07:46,659
Why did that name pop into my head?

124
00:07:47,400 --> 00:07:48,640
Since that is the case,

125
00:07:48,640 --> 00:07:49,880
you can stay for now.

126
00:07:50,440 --> 00:07:51,770
Once you've recovered,

127
00:07:52,240 --> 00:07:53,320
we'll decide what to do.

128
00:07:53,320 --> 00:07:54,640
Thank you, Sir.

129
00:08:08,120 --> 00:08:11,200
I knew all men in this world are like this.

130
00:08:11,280 --> 00:08:14,880
Act like an innocent flower, and they take the bait immediately.

131
00:08:17,760 --> 00:08:18,680
Oh no.

132
00:08:18,760 --> 00:08:21,120
I forgot to tell Sister Qingluan I went out to play.

133
00:08:21,120 --> 00:08:22,240
I haven't gone back yet.

134
00:08:22,240 --> 00:08:23,370
She must be worried.

135
00:08:38,080 --> 00:08:38,880
Master.

136
00:08:38,960 --> 00:08:41,679
You know this woman approached you with bad intentions.

137
00:08:41,679 --> 00:08:42,940
Why not drive her away?

138
00:08:43,400 --> 00:08:44,200
It's fine.

139
00:08:45,400 --> 00:08:47,320
She's just a little demon with weak spiritual power.

140
00:08:47,320 --> 00:08:48,980
She can't cause much trouble.

141
00:08:52,240 --> 00:08:53,320
Qingluan.

142
00:08:53,480 --> 00:08:54,880
Is Ling'er back yet?

143
00:08:55,000 --> 00:08:55,680
Brother.

144
00:08:58,920 --> 00:09:00,380
Weren't you in seclusion?

145
00:09:01,160 --> 00:09:03,160
I haven't seen Ling'er all day.

146
00:09:03,240 --> 00:09:04,900
She probably went out to play.

147
00:09:05,120 --> 00:09:07,040
Did I offend her earlier today?

148
00:09:07,480 --> 00:09:09,080
Is she too angry to come back?

149
00:09:10,120 --> 00:09:10,920
Brother.

150
00:09:13,840 --> 00:09:14,640
It's nothing.

151
00:09:15,720 --> 00:09:16,720
Sister Qingluan.

152
00:09:16,800 --> 00:09:17,600
I'm back.

153
00:09:24,640 --> 00:09:26,080
Yun Yuan is here too.

154
00:09:26,680 --> 00:09:27,640
So awkward.

155
00:09:28,080 --> 00:09:30,080
Didn't they say he's rarely around?

156
00:09:31,400 --> 00:09:32,400
Look at you.

157
00:09:32,640 --> 00:09:34,200
You went out to play without watching the time.

158
00:09:34,200 --> 00:09:35,720
What if you run into danger?

159
00:09:35,720 --> 00:09:36,520
Sister Qingluan.

160
00:09:36,520 --> 00:09:37,800
I came to tell you,

161
00:09:37,880 --> 00:09:40,240
I'm going to deal with a scoundrel soon,

162
00:09:40,520 --> 00:09:42,080
so I won't be back for a while.

163
00:09:42,080 --> 00:09:43,080
A scoundrel?

164
00:09:43,320 --> 00:09:44,000
Who is it?

165
00:09:44,440 --> 00:09:46,800
That son of the Heavenly Emperor.

166
00:09:47,040 --> 00:09:48,300
What's his name again?

167
00:09:49,440 --> 00:09:50,000
I forgot.

168
00:09:51,120 --> 00:09:53,440
Why are you provoking him for no reason?

169
00:09:53,920 --> 00:09:55,080
I don't know either.

170
00:09:55,320 --> 00:09:56,600
I just feel like,

171
00:09:57,080 --> 00:09:59,760
looking at him makes me uncomfortable.

172
00:10:00,560 --> 00:10:01,480
Qingluan.

173
00:10:01,880 --> 00:10:02,800
Brother.

174
00:10:03,520 --> 00:10:04,360
Give it to her.

175
00:10:04,720 --> 00:10:06,380
Let her do whatever she wants.

176
00:10:06,840 --> 00:10:07,480
Fine.

177
00:10:07,920 --> 00:10:09,520
If you insist on going, you can.

178
00:10:09,520 --> 00:10:12,240
This hairpin is a defensive spiritual artifact.

179
00:10:12,240 --> 00:10:13,840
You must wear it at all times.

180
00:10:14,240 --> 00:10:15,720
If you encounter danger,

181
00:10:15,920 --> 00:10:17,200
it will keep you safe.

182
00:10:18,120 --> 00:10:18,920
Okay, Sister.

183
00:10:18,920 --> 00:10:19,600
I promise you.

184
00:10:19,600 --> 00:10:21,000
I'll wear it at all times.

185
00:10:23,600 --> 00:10:25,080
I'm leaving now, Sister.

186
00:10:26,840 --> 00:10:27,880
See you, Yunyuan.

187
00:10:32,360 --> 00:10:33,080
Brother.

188
00:10:33,320 --> 00:10:35,800
You separated your Primordial Spirit and attached it to the hairpin.

189
00:10:35,800 --> 00:10:37,600
Will this harm you?

190
00:10:38,640 --> 00:10:39,440
It's fine.

191
00:10:40,120 --> 00:10:41,120
If I don't do this,

192
00:10:41,560 --> 00:10:43,890
I won't be at ease letting her go out alone.

193
00:10:45,800 --> 00:10:47,360
Even if you forget me,

194
00:10:47,840 --> 00:10:50,370
I will find a way to make you remember me again.

195
00:10:50,480 --> 00:10:51,010
Ling'er.

196
00:10:52,040 --> 00:10:53,640
It's good that you're awake.

197
00:10:57,360 --> 00:10:57,890
Brother.

198
00:11:27,880 --> 00:11:29,920
Yueying, take the Princess and leave first.

199
00:11:29,920 --> 00:11:31,080
If we leave, we leave together.

200
00:11:31,080 --> 00:11:32,600
Ling'er, you go first.

201
00:11:32,840 --> 00:11:33,970
I'll cover the rear.

202
00:11:34,000 --> 00:11:35,040
If we stay, we stay together.

203
00:11:35,040 --> 00:11:36,280
At worst, we fight to the death.

204
00:11:36,280 --> 00:11:37,600
Ling'er, listen to me.

205
00:11:41,280 --> 00:11:42,080
Go.

206
00:11:42,440 --> 00:11:44,040
Princess of the Dragon Clan.

207
00:11:44,400 --> 00:11:46,600
Do you think you can escape?

208
00:11:57,920 --> 00:11:58,640
Niannian.

209
00:12:03,000 --> 00:12:04,200
I'm going to kill you.

210
00:12:04,200 --> 00:12:04,730
Ling'er.

211
00:12:06,280 --> 00:12:08,840
Yunyuan, he ate Niannian's Primordial Spirit.

212
00:12:08,840 --> 00:12:10,300
I want to avenge Niannian.

213
00:12:10,640 --> 00:12:11,280
Ling'er.

214
00:12:12,640 --> 00:12:13,440
I promise you,

215
00:12:14,600 --> 00:12:16,600
I will definitely help you kill him.

216
00:12:17,160 --> 00:12:18,480
The Dragon Clan barrier.

217
00:12:18,480 --> 00:12:20,740
No one outside the Dragon Clan can enter.

218
00:12:20,800 --> 00:12:23,040
Unless someone opens the barrier from the inside,

219
00:12:23,040 --> 00:12:23,700
otherwise,

220
00:12:24,200 --> 00:12:26,000
how could you possibly break in?

221
00:12:27,800 --> 00:12:29,400
Yueying, I'll hold them off.

222
00:12:29,560 --> 00:12:31,160
Find a way to take Ling'er away.

223
00:12:31,160 --> 00:12:31,640
Rest assured, General.

224
00:12:31,640 --> 00:12:33,200
I will take the Princess to a safe place,

225
00:12:33,200 --> 00:12:33,880
and then come back to support you.

226
00:12:33,880 --> 00:12:34,320
Good.

227
00:12:34,480 --> 00:12:36,080
Princess of the Dragon Clan.

228
00:12:36,080 --> 00:12:37,940
If you hand over the Spirit Pearl,

229
00:12:38,440 --> 00:12:39,880
I will spare your life.

230
00:12:40,880 --> 00:12:41,840
Otherwise,

231
00:12:42,400 --> 00:12:43,560
let me think.

232
00:12:44,040 --> 00:12:45,960
Who should I eat next?

233
00:12:46,240 --> 00:12:47,080
You bastard.

234
00:12:47,200 --> 00:12:48,320
Let them go.

235
00:12:53,600 --> 00:12:55,120
This is the second one.

236
00:12:55,480 --> 00:12:56,560
Grandma Qi.

237
00:12:57,760 --> 00:12:58,960
Let me taste,

238
00:12:59,280 --> 00:13:00,720
what it's like.

239
00:13:02,160 --> 00:13:02,960
Don't!

240
00:13:10,000 --> 00:13:13,400
Will you hand it over or not?

241
00:13:14,400 --> 00:13:18,000
Li Sha, do you want to destroy the foundation of the Dragon Tribe?

242
00:13:18,160 --> 00:13:19,080
Of course,

243
00:13:20,240 --> 00:13:21,280
not.

244
00:13:21,800 --> 00:13:23,800
I am a man of my word.

245
00:13:25,480 --> 00:13:28,480
As long as you convince her to give up the Spirit Pearl,

246
00:13:28,840 --> 00:13:31,760
I promise that no one here

247
00:13:32,360 --> 00:13:33,800
wants to kill anyone.

248
00:13:34,200 --> 00:13:35,640
It's you, you traitor.

249
00:13:36,440 --> 00:13:37,240
Cousin.

250
00:13:38,040 --> 00:13:39,000
Why?

251
00:13:39,200 --> 00:13:40,440
So what if it is me?

252
00:13:40,720 --> 00:13:41,560
Why?

253
00:13:42,080 --> 00:13:43,560
Just because of a pearl?

254
00:13:43,640 --> 00:13:45,960
You are nothing but a useless waste.

255
00:13:46,240 --> 00:13:48,280
You, become the Dragon Lord?

256
00:13:48,760 --> 00:13:49,820
You're not worthy.

257
00:13:50,080 --> 00:13:53,280
Why must I be forced to kneel at your feet?

258
00:13:53,520 --> 00:13:55,280
If you were capable of being the Dragon Lord,

259
00:13:55,280 --> 00:13:56,960
I would have gladly stepped aside.

260
00:13:56,960 --> 00:13:58,360
But I never expected you to commit

261
00:13:58,360 --> 00:14:00,080
such an act of betrayal.

262
00:14:00,320 --> 00:14:01,600
Betrayal?

263
00:14:03,720 --> 00:14:04,520
Ao Ling,

264
00:14:05,640 --> 00:14:06,700
you piece of trash.

265
00:14:07,000 --> 00:14:08,320
You deserve to die.

266
00:14:09,640 --> 00:14:10,480
At this point,

267
00:14:10,480 --> 00:14:12,040
why waste words with them?

268
00:14:12,360 --> 00:14:14,020
Princess of the Dragon Tribe,

269
00:14:14,040 --> 00:14:15,600
I'll say it again.

270
00:14:15,960 --> 00:14:18,220
As long as you hand over the Spirit Pearl,

271
00:14:18,400 --> 00:14:20,320
I will spare your life.

272
00:14:21,240 --> 00:14:23,440
As for the squabbles within your tribe,

273
00:14:23,960 --> 00:14:25,880
I have no interest.

274
00:14:58,400 --> 00:14:59,200
Ling'er.

275
00:15:00,800 --> 00:15:01,600
Ling'er.

276
00:15:02,120 --> 00:15:04,040
Ling'er, what are you doing?

277
00:15:06,480 --> 00:15:08,680
If not for this Spirit Pearl within me,

278
00:15:08,720 --> 00:15:11,240
our people wouldn't suffer this calamity.

279
00:15:11,720 --> 00:15:12,520
Yun Yuan,

280
00:15:13,640 --> 00:15:14,440
live on.

281
00:15:14,640 --> 00:15:16,280
Ling'er, get down!

282
00:15:20,400 --> 00:15:21,440
With my soul,

283
00:15:22,120 --> 00:15:23,280
enter your spirit,

284
00:15:24,040 --> 00:15:25,320
protect my people,

285
00:15:26,240 --> 00:15:28,320
and bless the world.

286
00:15:45,560 --> 00:15:47,080
Ling'er!

287
00:15:47,440 --> 00:15:48,480
Yun Yuan!

288
00:15:48,880 --> 00:15:49,560
General!

289
00:15:50,080 --> 00:15:50,840
Yun Yuan...

290
00:15:51,040 --> 00:15:52,680
Ling'er, I'm here.

291
00:15:52,840 --> 00:15:54,120
I did it.

292
00:15:54,640 --> 00:15:55,560
You did it.

293
00:15:55,960 --> 00:15:56,760
Ling'er,

294
00:15:57,040 --> 00:15:57,900
let me heal you.

295
00:16:03,000 --> 00:16:03,800
Yun Yuan,

296
00:16:04,040 --> 00:16:04,840
it's no use.

297
00:16:06,520 --> 00:16:08,360
The Spirit Pearl is shattered.

298
00:16:11,240 --> 00:16:12,520
You can't save me.

299
00:16:14,720 --> 00:16:16,480
Ling'er, I can.

300
00:16:17,320 --> 00:16:19,320
I can definitely save you, Ling'er.

301
00:16:19,320 --> 00:16:20,200
Promise me.

302
00:16:20,520 --> 00:16:21,880
I promise you anything.

303
00:16:22,520 --> 00:16:24,080
Live well.

304
00:16:26,520 --> 00:16:29,040
Don't grieve for me.

305
00:16:29,760 --> 00:16:30,640
Yun Yuan,

306
00:16:31,080 --> 00:16:31,880
Ling'er.

307
00:16:32,000 --> 00:16:36,520
you said Kunmi is beautiful.

308
00:16:38,200 --> 00:16:40,880
Take me to see it.

309
00:16:42,320 --> 00:16:43,920
I'll take you, Ling'er.

310
00:16:44,360 --> 00:16:45,690
I'll take you right now.

311
00:16:55,680 --> 00:16:56,320
Ling'er?

312
00:16:58,160 --> 00:16:58,960
Ling'er!

313
00:16:59,840 --> 00:17:00,640
Ling'er!

314
00:17:01,880 --> 00:17:03,960
Ling'er.
